;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_1
;[exp] onObjectTrigger

@roadguide w=Exit e="Tool Shed"

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_2
;[exp] true

@delevent
@addevent map=温泉・脱衣所 num=11
@addevent map=温泉・浴場 num=7
@addevent map=温泉・浴場 num=8
@wait time=500
@walk move=n
@wait time=500
[texton]
[キャラ f=05]「This is...!」[k]
When I entered the hole in the middle of the cliff, I found a cave with neatly arranged walls inside.[k]
There are well-used construction tools scattered around. Could it be a mine shaft or something?[k]
[if exp='ELF || SYL'][キャラ f=06]「...There's no way to go back, so I guess I'll just have to go and see.」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM || DWA || GNO'][キャラ f=05]「...There is no way to go back, so I think it's worth moving forward.」[k]
[endif]
If this was a mine tunnel, there must be an exit that workers would have used. Thinking this, we walked deeper into the cave in search of an exit.[k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_3
;[exp] true

@delevent
[texton]
[キャラ]'s group walk through the cave naked. The air inside the cave is cool, and they can't help but shiver.[k]
[if exp='ELF2'][キャラ f=32]「It's so embarrassing to wander around a cave naked...」[k]
[elsif exp='SYL2'][キャラ f=28]「I feel really embarrassed walking around a cave naked.」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM2'][キャラ f=29]「Walking naked in a cave is really embarrassing...」[k]
[elsif exp='DWA2'][キャラ f=29]「Walking naked in a cave is very embarrassing.」[k]
[elsif exp='GNO2'][キャラ f=25]「It's kind of embarrassing to walk around naked in a cave...」[k]
[endif]
No one is watching us naked right now.[r]
...I understand that, but I couldn't help feeling uneasy about doing so in a place where people don't normally walk around naked.[k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
